Combine rice, chicken, tomato, cilantro, green onions, and avocado together in a bowl. Whisk canola oil, lime juice, lime zest, garlic, jalapeno pepper, salt, oregano, cumin, and chili powder together in a bowl; pour over rice mixture and toss to coat. Chill in refrigerator, about 1 hour. Place lettuce in a serving bowl; top with rice mixture.